   NEVER SETTLE

   ATU empowers you to embrace your inner grit and determination.




IT'S NOT ABOUT WHERE YOU COME FROM

   It's about where you end up.

   There’s an overachieving spirit here at Arkansas Tech University. We’re
   never content with the the way things are. We’re always striving,
   reaching, working toward a better tomorrow. Our alumni never settle for
   less than the best from themselves. Our faculty never settles for less
   than the best from our students. Our students never settle for less
   than the best from their university.




   #1 for Arkansans studying STEM

   18:1 Student to Faculty Ratio

   3rd Largest University in Arkansas
