   ATU AWARDS MORE STEM DEGREES TO ARKANSANS THAN ANY OTHER UNIVERSITY
   two students working in the English writing lab

   ATU'S MASTER OF ARTS IN ENGLISH DEGREE WAS RANKED SEVENTH IN THE NATION
