NEVER SETTLE

   All of this rolls into a total college experience not found anywhere
   else in the nation. And it sets you up for success right after
   graduation. It’s why Arkansas Tech University was ranked the No. 1
   college for upward social mobility in Arkansas and why we have alumni
   working in 35 different countries around the world.


